+   // ===========================================================================
+   // Update Deal Lead
+   // ===========================================================================
+   
+   async updateDealLead(id: string, newLeadId: string): Promise&lt;Deal&gt; {
+     // Verify deal exists
+     const deal = await this.getDealById(id);
+     
+     // Verify new lead exists
+     const lead = await db.queryOne&lt;Lead&gt;(
+       'SELECT * FROM leads WHERE id = $1',
+       [newLeadId]
+     );
+     
+     if (!lead) {
+       throw new NotFoundError('Lead', newLeadId);
+     }
+     
+     // Check if there's already a deal for this lead in this pipeline
+     const existingDeal = await db.queryOne&lt;Deal&gt;(
+       'SELECT * FROM deals WHERE lead_id = $1 AND pipeline_id = $2 AND id != $3',
+       [newLeadId, deal.pipeline_id, id]
+     );
+     
+     if (existingDeal) {
+       throw new ConflictError('A deal already exists for this lead in this pipeline', {
+         existing_deal_id: existingDeal.id
+       });
+     }
+     
+     // Update deal name based on new lead
+     const dealName = &#96;${lead.first_name || ''} ${lead.last_name || ''} - ${lead.email}&#96;.trim();
+     
+     const updatedDeal = await db.queryOne&lt;Deal&gt;(
+       &#96;UPDATE deals 
+        SET lead_id = $1, name = $2, updated_at = NOW()
+        WHERE id = $3
+        RETURNING *&#96;,
+       [newLeadId, dealName, id]
+     );
+     
+     return updatedDeal!;
+   }
  
    // ===========================================================================

+     Params: IdParams;
+     Body: { lead_id: string };
+   }&gt;(
+     '/deals/:id/lead',
+     {
+       preHandler: validateApiKey,

+         description: 'Update the lead associated with a deal',
+         tags: ['Deals'],
+         params: {
+           type: 'object',
+           required: ['id'],
+           properties: {
+             id: { type: 'string', format: 'uuid' }
+           }
+         },
+         body: {
+           type: 'object',
+           required: ['lead_id'],
+           properties: {
+             lead_id: { type: 'string', format: 'uuid' }

+             type: 'object',

+           validationErrors: paramResult.error.errors
+         });

+       const deal = await dealService.updateDealLead(paramResult.data.id, bodyResult.data.lead_id);

+         dealId: deal.id,
+         newLeadId: bodyResult.data.lead_id
+       }, 'Deal lead updated');

+  * @param {string} leadId - New Lead UUID
+  * @returns {Promise&lt;Object&gt;} Updated deal
+  */
+ export const updateDealLead = async (dealId, leadId) =&gt; {
+   const { json } = await httpClient(&#96;${API_URL}/deals/${dealId}/lead&#96;, {
+     method: 'PATCH',
+     body: JSON.stringify({ lead_id: leadId }),
+   });
+   return json;
